<Defs>
	<AlienRace.ThingDef_AlienRace ParentName="ESCP_BaseRace_MerStandardHead">
		<defName>ESCP_AltmerRace</defName>
		<label>Altmer</label>
		<description>An elven race, considered to be the closest living race to the Aldmer. The Altmer consider themselves to be the pinnacle of culture, often believing that all other races are uncivilised. Other races consider the Altmer to be extremely arrogant and abrasive.\n\nWhile Altmer may be renowned for their superior intellect and creativity, though are also well known to be somewhat frail. Thankfully their skill with magic, and their use of goblin slave armies, more than makes up for this weakness.\n\n&lt;color=#E5E54C&gt;Mer Blood&lt;/color&gt;\nPsychic sensitivity is increased by 20%\nFertility is decreased by 50%.\nBase health scale is decreased by 20%\nLife expectancy is increased to 300 years.\n\n&lt;color=#E5E54C&gt;Aldmer&lt;/color&gt;\nPsychic sensitivity is increased by an additional 30%\nBase health scale is decreased by an additional 10%.\nFlammability is increased by 20%.\nImmunity gain speed is increased by 25%.\nGlobal learning factor is increased by 20%.\nExpectations are increased by one level.</description>
		<descriptionHyperlinks>
			<GeneDef MayRequire="Ludeon.RimWorld.Biotech">ESCP_GeneInheritedBonus_Mer</GeneDef>
			<GeneDef MayRequire="Ludeon.RimWorld.Biotech">ESCP_GeneInheritedBonus_Altmer</GeneDef>
		</descriptionHyperlinks>
		<modExtensions>
			<li Class="ESCP_RaceTools.RaceProperties">
				<modifiedExpectations>true</modifiedExpectations>
				<expectationOffset>1</expectationOffset>
				<majorRacialGeneToInherit MayRequire="Ludeon.RimWorld.Biotech">ESCP_GeneInheritedBonus_Mer</majorRacialGeneToInherit>
				<minorRacialGeneToInherit MayRequire="Ludeon.RimWorld.Biotech">ESCP_GeneInheritedBonus_Altmer</minorRacialGeneToInherit>
			</li>
		</modExtensions>
		<statBases>
			<PsychicSensitivity>1.5</PsychicSensitivity>
			<Flammability>1.2</Flammability>
			<ImmunityGainSpeed>1.25</ImmunityGainSpeed>
